    {
        "content": "<p>I am now convinced that <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/pull/5147\">lean4#5147</a> is the best solution to the problems encountered at <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/16096\">#16096</a></p>",
